<a href="/articles/27132.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27132/indexMediumPc2/27132.jpg?1463727053" alt="三星支付搭伙支付宝，银联大概不太高兴">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/4/medium/4.png?1411569452" alt="智能">
			<span>智能</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">三星支付搭伙支付宝，银联大概不太高兴</h1>
